2076
02:26:59,555 --> 02:27:00,554
Kiri.

2077
02:27:03,560 --> 02:27:05,142
Ouve as minhas palavras.

2078
02:27:06,020 --> 02:27:09,021
Se houver algo
que possas fazer...

2079
02:27:10,775 --> 02:27:12,817
