2124
02:30:57,841 --> 02:30:59,173
E não são.

2125
02:31:00,218 --> 02:31:01,300
Habitualmente.

2126
02:31:02,051 --> 02:31:04,801
Payakan, vou à frente.

2127
02:31:05,138 --> 02:31:07,180
Sim, Matriarca.

2128
02:31:11,812 --> 02:31:13,353
<i>Perdi o contacto visual.</i>

2129
02:31:43,011 --> 02:31:44,468
Eles estão a lutar!

2130
02:31:44,554 --> 02:31:46,220
Sim! Sim!

2131
02:32:01,654 --> 02:32:03,319
Por aqui! Para a escotilha!

2132
02:32:10,288 --> 02:32:11,328
Agora!

2133
02:32:41,237 --> 02:32:42,278
Cuidado!

2134
02:33:04,384 --> 02:33:05,842
Armas a postos!

2135
02:33:05,928 --> 02:33:07,177
Abrir fogo!

2136
02:33:32,539 --> 02:33:33,538
Bombordo!

2137
02:33:38,879 --> 02:33:39,878
Recarregar.

2138
02:33:40,381 --> 02:33:41,380
Cuidado!

2139
02:34:14,457 --> 02:34:15,706
Boa, Jake.

2140
02:34:15,792 --> 02:34:16,957
Mano, olha.

2141
02:34:29,013 --> 02:34:30,012
Sim!

2142
02:34:30,097 --> 02:34:31,096
Sim!

2143
02:34:45,446 --> 02:34:46,445
Jake.

2144
02:34:50,659 --> 02:34:51,866
São as Cinzas.

2145
02:34:52,829 --> 02:34:53,493
Aproximam-se inimigos

2146
02:34:53,705 --> 02:34:54,619
em banshees.

2147
02:34:54,706 --> 02:34:55,955
Mais de cem.

2148
02:34:56,040 --> 02:34:58,165
São amigáveis.
Têm distintivos IFF.

2149
02:34:58,251 --> 02:34:59,250
São dos nossos.

2150
02:34:59,336 --> 02:35:01,794
Obrigado por ter feito
sair o Sully, General.

2151
02:35:01,879 --> 02:35:03,337
Agora trato eu disto.

2152
02:35:40,044 --> 02:35:41,293
É impossível ganharem.

2153
02:35:42,545 --> 02:35:43,836
Estão a morrer.

2154
02:35:45,924 --> 02:35:46,923
Kiri!

2155
02:35:47,009 --> 02:35:48,216
Kiri!

2156
02:35:48,761 --> 02:35:50,802
- Para-a!
- Kiri, para.

2157
02:35:51,555 --> 02:35:53,013
- Kiri.
- Para. Volta...

2158
02:35:53,098 --> 02:35:54,680
